GG_Tele
By Harlequiine

A different gungame map, very original compared to all the others coming out recently.
A set of glass walls lined up, connected via teleporters.
It is more amateur-ish than my other maps, and can become quite buggy when there are too many players, but I find it to be very fun.

Recommended for 6-14 players.
